{"tid":461313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好憎我屋企","createTime":"2017-11-07T12:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T13:37:00.000Z","uid":78536,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f0df0301f98b6ffd7618072fd678597b2df9e36b","tid":461313,"uid":78536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:57:37.000Z","msg":"買個蛋糕十幾蚊大大個飯幾幾日話敗家<br />\n自己買成千蚊幾衫<br />\n個寶貝仔真敗家就聲都唔聲<br />\n揾揾埋先比一成家用<br />\n我比一半都話我比得少 (利伸比過萬）<br />\n真心好想死"},{"pid":"122d435cf7e739340bbc6bb9c56063b5a5198f30","tid":461313,"uid":78536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:58:51.000Z","msg":"食幾日"},{"pid":"bfb3431e74af8b144d2c31c5bdecdd6f8815af12","tid":461313,"uid":1590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:59:43.000Z","msg":"世界級重男輕女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e45177b82e31e58e520a44af7772196dd946fe8","tid":461313,"uid":84355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"搬出去啦"},{"pid":"f2eba0f41d1ed7ed0d0226408e2011777d9cf75f","tid":461313,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搬出去啦</blockquote><br />\n+1"},{"pid":"10d9d680db46b144c2fb48760b16b97c1f8ba216","tid":461313,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"個萬幾幫人交租都唔益你個傻鳩老豆老母<br />\n你仲比家用仲傻鳩"},{"pid":"b529aaca5aa743285602295d0b625fc0ad56d09f","tid":461313,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"609d2e0dc837d49f01c061deaa4e28de05e96613","tid":461313,"uid":117405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"駛乜死，搬出去一了百了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23dd7d9bb5a6dce8890c8d7862a4a658bc41fbb","tid":461313,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:04:49.000Z","msg":"搬出去，比少一半家用，佢哋唔收就算，直接唔比"},{"pid":"bb8f71ede2e8fb26ce9049fa9b37c30fd19f757f","tid":461313,"uid":78536,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:06:12.000Z","msg":"試過搬啦 雖然係交租 始終有種寄下籬下的感覺<br />\n而且 其實我好唔捨得我屋企 雖然佢地對我真係好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今個月遲左比家用已經寸到我死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b129201b58373f6a5f06d35bb75bcbf71041e0a","tid":461313,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:06:49.000Z","msg":"搬出去啦。識好多人搬出去後搵到自己嘅第一桶金，佢哋嘅屋企人又會黐返埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過到時千祈唔好心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ae8e2b08f2182bac201d8741eb1e166d61483d","tid":461313,"uid":13184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89648e86e54ac19320d66ff6f0e4ad10cbfcce60","tid":461313,"uid":78536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搬出去，比少一半家用，佢哋唔收就算，直接唔比</blockquote><br />\n比少一個崩都屌你垃圾廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49894e0544b43c53c4ef7182c9b454e18acaed1a","tid":461313,"uid":106149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:08:02.000Z","msg":"打鑊金佢地啦"},{"pid":"a91a54c6996fa381c411be9d95d05c04f75887c9","tid":461313,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"530b23c6b199551902812dd98939350f2237748b","tid":461313,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"假膠 ? 唔過萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144e081b670a1189616123060e7bda826dd4cb8b","tid":461313,"uid":123137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過搬啦 雖然係交租 始終有種寄下籬下的感覺<br />\n而且 其實我好唔捨得我屋企 雖然佢地對我真係好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今個月遲左比家用已經寸到我死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係個句野<br />\n無論屋企人定係出面人<br />\n做係&quot;淋&quot;善果個 佢地一定會食住你<br />\n反而你決絕D,做個仆街仔/女<br />\n佢地反而對你更加好,<br />\n而家佢地知道就算對你幾衰,你都一樣比咁多家用,唔恰你恰邊個?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界就係咁現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:過來人,而家食住佢地"},{"pid":"2f417ef42600015ead5ae7a2d238e0aeb9b6b019","tid":461313,"uid":78536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搬出去，比少一半家用，佢哋唔收就算，直接唔比</blockquote><br />\n比少一個崩都屌你垃圾廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有講錯咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人恰到心口都仲留係到</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n諗返起細個都叫曾經對過我好就好唔捨得<br />\n始終係屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都知我無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848e7657993b2fa0200d7188a4d1ceb83baf0a11","tid":461313,"uid":76969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過搬啦 雖然係交租 始終有種寄下籬下的感覺<br />\n而且 其實我好唔捨得我屋企 雖然佢地對我真係好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今個月遲左比家用已經寸到我死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條路自己揀 仆街唔好喊"},{"pid":"2d01cd5ac88cf723f79a7c3d774bb2bde9668ca5","tid":461313,"uid":78536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過搬啦 雖然係交租 始終有種寄下籬下的感覺<br />\n而且 其實我好唔捨得我屋企 雖然佢地對我真係好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今個月遲左比家用已經寸到我死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係個句野<br />\n無論屋企人定係出面人<br />\n做係&quot;淋&quot;善果個 佢地一定會食住你<br />\n反而你決絕D,做個仆街仔/女<br />\n佢地反而對你更加好,<br />\n而家佢地知道就算對你幾衰,你都一樣比咁多家用,唔恰你恰邊個?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界就係咁現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:過來人,而家食住佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家已經唔同佢地講野同會講mean野但無仼何效用 <br />\n利申講完會內心屌自己唔應該感講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0e26841e4c2bf6bf60f7f544d27b9fe1cfdc58","tid":461313,"uid":123137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試過搬啦 雖然係交租 始終有種寄下籬下的感覺<br />\n而且 其實我好唔捨得我屋企 雖然佢地對我真係好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今個月遲左比家用已經寸到我死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係個句野<br />\n無論屋企人定係出面人<br />\n做係&quot;淋&quot;善果個 佢地一定會食住你<br />\n反而你決絕D,做個仆街仔/女<br />\n佢地反而對你更加好,<br />\n而家佢地知道就算對你幾衰,你都一樣比咁多家用,唔恰你恰邊個?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界就係咁現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:過來人,而家食住佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\